  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Scout-Nin Keyword: Specialized </p><p>You may spend a Superiority Die targeting one allied creature within 30 feet of you.</p><p>When you do, the next time they would make an attack of any type, they add half the result of the Superiority Die to the attack roll.</p><p>On a successful hit of the allied creatures attack, if you make the same type of attack, targeting the same creature, on your next turn, you add the same Superiority Die to your attack roll.</p><p></p>",
